#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please report any problems or feature requests to the <ulink url=\"https://"
"bugs.kde.org/\">&kde; Bug Tracking System</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Prijavite morebitne težave ali zahteve po funkcijah na <ulink url=\"https://"
"bugs.kde.org/\">&kde; Sistem za sledenje napakam</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &spectacle;"
msgstr "Zagon &spectacle;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "&spectacle; can be started in a variety of ways, as described below:"
msgstr "&spectacle; se lahko začne na različne načine, kot je opisano spodaj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the application launcher menu, &spectacle; can be found at "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Applications</guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Utilities</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Screenshot Capture Utility &spectacle;</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"V meniju zaganjalnika aplikacij &spectacle; najdete v "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Aplikacije</guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Pripomočki</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Pripomoček za zajem posnetkov zaslona &spectacle;</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing the <keysym>Print Screen</keysym> button on the keyboard (often "
"labeled <keycap>PrtSc</keycap>, <keycap>PrtScn</keycap> or similar) will "
"immediately launch &spectacle;. Additionally, three more keyboard shortcuts "
"are available to take screenshots and save them in your default save folder "
"without showing the &GUI;:"
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete gumb <keysym>Print Screen</keysym> na tipkovnici (pogosto "
"označen kot <keycap>PrtSc</keycap>, <keycap>PrtScn</keycap> ali podobno), se "
"takoj zažene &spectacle;. Poleg tega so na voljo še tri bližnjice na "
"tipkovnici za snemanje posnetkov zaslona in njihovo shranjevanje v privzeto "
"mapo za shranjevanje brez prikaza &GUI;:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Meta</keycap><keysym>Print Screen</"
"keysym></keycombo> will take a screenshot of the active window"
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Meta</keycap><keysym>Print Screen</"
"keysym></keycombo> bo naredil posnetek zaslona aktivnega okna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keysym>Print Screen</keysym></keycombo> "
"will take a screenshot of your entire desktop, &ie; all monitors"
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keysym>Print Screen</keysym></keycombo> "
"posname posnetek zaslona vašega celotnega namizja (vsi monitorji)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Meta</keycap>&Shift;<keysym>Print Screen</"
"keysym></keycombo> will take a rectangular region screenshot"
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Meta</keycap>&Shift;<keysym>Print Screen</"
"keysym></keycombo> bo naredil posnetek zaslona pravokotne regije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure the default save location and filename by starting "
"&spectacle; normally and clicking on the <guibutton>Configure...</guibutton> "
"button, then navigating to the Save section."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto mesto shranjevanja in ime datoteke lahko konfigurirate tako, da "
"zaženete &spectacle; in kliknite gumb <guibutton>Konfiguriraj...</"
"guibutton>, nato pa se pomaknite do razdelka Shrani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mini command line &krunner; (invoked with <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>) may also be used to start "
"&spectacle;."
msgstr ""
"Mini ukazna vrstica &krunner; (priklicano s <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>) lahko uporabite tudi za zagon &spectacle;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&spectacle; can be started from the command-line. &spectacle; has an "
"extensive set of command-line options, including a background mode which can "
"be used to script the capture of screenshots without showing the &GUI; or "
"requiring user interaction."
msgstr ""
"&spectacle; lahko zaženete iz ukazne vrstice. &spectacle; ima obsežen nabor "
"možnosti ukazne vrstice, vključno z načinom v ozadju, ki ga je mogoče "
"uporabiti za skript za zajem posnetkov zaslona brez prikaza &GUI; ali "
"zahteva interakcijo uporabnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "To start &spectacle; from the command prompt, type in:"
msgstr "Za zagon &spectacle; v ukazni vrstici vnesite:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>%</prompt> <command>spectacle &amp;</command>"
msgstr "<prompt>%</prompt> <command>spectacle &amp;</command>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view the full list of command-line options and their explanation, type in:"
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati celoten seznam možnosti ukazne vrstice in njihovo "
"razlago, vnesite:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>%</prompt> <command>spectacle --help</command>"
msgstr "<prompt>%</prompt> <command>spectacle --help</command>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &spectacle;"
msgstr "Uporaba &spectacle;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Once &spectacle; starts, you will see a window like the following:"
msgstr "Ko zaženete &spectacle;, boste videli takšno okno:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "&spectacle; Main Window"
msgstr "&spectacle; Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&spectacle; grabs an image of your entire desktop immediately after it is "
"started, but before it displays itself on screen. This allows you to quickly "
"create full-desktop screenshot images."
msgstr ""
"&spectacle; zajame sliko vašega celotnega namizja takoj po zagonu, vendar "
"preden se prikaže na zaslonu. To vam omogoča hitro ustvarjanje slik zaslona "
"celotnega namizja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The snapshot taken by &spectacle; is displayed in the preview window, which "
"is located on the left-hand side of the &spectacle; application window."
msgstr ""
"Posnetek, ki ga je posnel &spectacle; se prikaže v oknu za predogled, ki se "
"nahaja na levi strani &spectacle; okna aplikacije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The image can be saved to a location of your choice by clicking on the "
"<guibutton>Save As</guibutton> button or typing <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>. This opens the standard save "
"dialog, where you can choose the filename, the folder location, and the "
"format that your screenshot will be saved in. You may edit the filename to "
"anything you wish, including the name of a previously saved screenshot."
msgstr ""
"Sliko lahko shranite na želeno mesto s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Shrani kot</"
"guibutton> ali tipkanjem <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</"
"keycap></keycombo >. S tem se odpre standardno pogovorno okno za "
"shranjevanje, kjer lahko izberete ime datoteke, lokacijo mape in obliko, v "
"kateri bo shranjen vaš posnetek zaslona. Ime datoteke lahko spremenite na "
"karkoli si želite, vključno z imenom predhodno shranjenega posnetka zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To save a screenshot to the default location, click on the arrow portion of "
"the <guibutton>Save As...</guibutton> button and press the <guimenuitem>Save "
"</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo>) button. The new save mode will be remembered for next time. The "
"default save location and filename can be configured, as described later."
msgstr ""
"Če želite posnetek zaslona shraniti na privzeto mesto, kliknite puščični del "
"gumba <guibutton>Shrani kot...</guibutton> in pritisnite <guimenuitem>Shrani "
"</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo>). Nov način shranjevanja si bo zapomnil za naslednjič. Privzeto "
"mesto shranjevanja in ime datoteke je mogoče konfigurirati, kot je opisano "
"kasneje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To quickly save the image and quit &spectacle;, click on the checkbox beside "
"<guilabel>Quit after manual Save or Copy</guilabel>, then click the arrow "
"portion of the <guibutton>Save As...</guibutton> button and press the "
"<guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</"
"keycap></keycombo>) item. This saves the image as a PNG file in your default "
"<filename class=\"directory\">Pictures</filename> folder, and exits the "
"application immediately. As above, this new save mode will be remembered."
msgstr ""
"Če želite hitro shraniti sliko in zapreti &spectacle;, kliknite potrditveno "
"polje poleg <guilabel>Zapri po ročnem shranjevanju ali kopiranju</guilabel>, "
"nato kliknite puščični del gumba <guibutton>Shrani kot...</guibutton> in "
"pritisnite element <guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>). To shrani sliko kot datoteko "
"PNG v vašo privzeto mapo <filename class=\"directory\">Pictures</filename> "
"in takoj zapre aplikacijo. Kot zgoraj, bo ta novi način shranjevanja "
"zapomnjen za naslednjič."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Taking A Screenshot"
msgstr "Zajem posnetka zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you open &spectacle;, it immediately takes a screenshot, unless "
"otherwise set in the general options, of the whole screen as a convenience "
"and shows a preview of it in the main window. You can save this screenshot "
"using the buttons on the bottom of the window, or take a new one using the "
"controls to the right of the preview."
msgstr ""
"Ko odprete &spectacle;, zaradi priročnosti takoj naredi posnetek celotnega "
"zaslona, razen če ni drugače nastavljeno v splošnih možnostih, in prikaže "
"predogled v glavnem oknu. Ta posnetek zaslona lahko shranite z gumbi na dnu "
"okna ali posnamete novega s kontrolniki na desni strani predogleda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To discard the current screenshot and take another screenshot, press the "
"<guibutton>Take a New Screenshot</guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>) button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zavreči trenutni posnetek zaslona in narediti nov posnetek "
"zaslona, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Naredi nov posnetek zaslona</guibutton> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After capturing a screenshot, &spectacle; will show you an info panel with a "
"link to the screenshot file and propose you to <guibutton>Open Containing "
"Folder</guibutton> of this file."
msgstr ""
"Po zajemu posnetka zaslona vam bo &spectacle; prikazal informacijsko ploščo "
"s povezavo do datoteke posnetka zaslona in vam predlagal, da "
"<guibutton>Odprete mapo, ki vsebuje</guibutton> te datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may configure certain options on the right hand side of the application "
"window before taking a new screenshot. These options allow you to select the "
"area of the screen that is to be captured, set a delay before capturing the "
"image, and configure whether the mouse cursor and/or the window decorations "
"should be captured along with the screenshot."
msgstr ""
"Preden naredite nov posnetek zaslona, lahko konfigurirate določene možnosti "
"na desni strani okna aplikacije. Te možnosti vam omogočajo, da izberete "
"območje zaslona, ki ga želite zajeti, nastavite zakasnitev pred zajemom "
"slike in konfigurirate, ali naj se miškin kazalec in/ali okraski okna "
"zajamejo skupaj s posnetkom zaslona."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Capture Mode"
msgstr "Način zajemanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The capture mode settings allow you to set the area of the screen that "
"should be captured, and whether there should be a delay between pressing the "
"<guibutton>Take a New Screenshot</guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>) button and taking the screenshot. "
"You may also enable the <guilabel>On Click</guilabel> checkbox, which "
"disables the delay function and only takes the screenshot after you click "
"anywhere on the screen after clicking the <guibutton>Take a New Screenshot</"
"guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>) "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve načina zajema vam omogočajo, da nastavite območje zaslona, ki naj "
"bo zajeto, in ali naj pride do zamika med pritiskom <guibutton>Naredi nov "
"posnetek zaslona</guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</"
"keycap></keycombo>) in naredite posnetek zaslona. Omogočite lahko tudi "
"potrditveno polje <guilabel>Ob kliku</guilabel>, ki onemogoči funkcijo "
"zakasnitve in naredi posnetek zaslona šele, ko kliknete kjer koli na zaslonu "
"po kliku <guibutton>Naredi nov posnetek zaslona</guibutton> (<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Area</guilabel> combo-box allows you to set the area of the "
"screen that should be captured. There are five options to select from, as "
"described below."
msgstr ""
"Kombinirano polje <guilabel>Območje</guilabel> vam omogoča, da nastavite "
"območje zaslona, ki naj bo zajeto. Izbirate lahko med petimi možnostmi, kot "
"je opisano spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Full Screen (All Monitors)</guilabel> option takes a "
"screenshot of your entire desktop, spread across all the outputs, including "
"all the monitors, projectors etc."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Celozaslonski (vsi monitorji)</guilabel> naredi posnetek "
"zaslona vašega celotnega namizja, razporejenega po vseh izhodih, vključno z "
"vsemi monitorji, projektorji itd."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Current Screen</guilabel> option takes a screenshot of the "
"output that currently contains the mouse pointer."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Trenutni zaslon</guilabel> naredi posnetek zaslona izhoda, "
"ki trenutno vsebuje kazalec miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Rectangular Region</guilabel> option allows you to select a "
"rectangular region of your desktop with your mouse. This region may be "
"spread across different outputs."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Pravokotna regija</guilabel> vam omogoča, da z miško "
"izberete pravokotno regijo namizja. Ta regija je lahko razpršena po "
"različnih izhodih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This mode does not immediately take a screenshot but allows you to draw a "
"rectangle on your screen, which can be moved and resized as needed. Once the "
"desired selection rectangle has been drawn, double-clicking anywhere on the "
"screen, or pressing the &Enter; button on the keyboard will capture the "
"screenshot."
msgstr ""
"Ta način ne naredi takoj posnetka zaslona, ampak vam omogoča, da na zaslonu "
"narišete pravokotnik, ki ga lahko po potrebi premikate in spreminjate "
"velikost. Ko je želeni izbirni pravokotnik narisan, dvokliknite kjer koli na "
"zaslonu ali pritisnite na &Enter; gumb na tipkovnici za zajem zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the arrow keys to move and adjust the rectangle. Pressing the "
"arrow keys will move the rectangle. Holding the &Shift; key while pressing "
"the arrow keys will move the rectangle slowly, for fine-tuning your "
"selection. Holding the &Alt; key while pressing the arrow keys will adjust "
"the size of the rectangle."
msgstr ""
"S puščičnimi tipkami lahko premikate in prilagajate pravokotnik. S pritiskom "
"na puščične tipke premaknete pravokotnik. Držite &Shift; medtem ko "
"pritisnete puščične tipke, bo pravokotnik počasi premikal za natančno "
"nastavitev izbire. Držite &Alt; tipko, medtem ko pritiskate puščične tipke, "
"prilagodite velikost pravokotnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Active Window</guilabel> option takes a screenshot of the "
"window that currently has focus. It is advisable to use a delay with this "
"mode, to give you time to select and activate a window before the screenshot "
"is taken."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Aktivno okno</guilabel> naredi posnetek zaslona okna, ki "
"je trenutno v fokusu. Pri tem načinu je priporočljivo uporabiti zakasnitev, "
"da imate čas, da izberete in aktivirate okno, preden se naredi posnetek "
"zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Window Under Cursor</guilabel> option takes a screenshot of "
"the window that is under the mouse cursor. If the cursor is on top of a "
"popup menu, &spectacle; tries to take a screenshot of the menu as well as "
"its parent window."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Okno pod kazalcem</guilabel> naredi posnetek zaslona okna, "
"ki je pod kazalcem miške. Če je kazalec na vrhu pojavnega menija, "
"&spectacle; poskuša narediti posnetek zaslona menija in njegovega "
"nadrejenega okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While this works most of the time, in certain cases it may fail to obtain "
"information about the parent window. In this case, &spectacle; falls back to "
"old way of capturing the image automatically, and captures an image of only "
"the popup menu. You can also force the old way of capturing the image by "
"checking the <guilabel>Capture the current pop-up only</guilabel> checkbox "
"under <guilabel>Options</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Čeprav to večinoma deluje, v določenih primerih morda ne uspe pridobiti "
"informacij o nadrejenem oknu. V tem primeru se &spectacle; vrne na stari "
"način samodejnega zajemanja slike in zajame samo sliko pojavnega menija. "
"Lahko tudi vsilite stari način zajema slike, tako da označite potrditveno "
"polje <guilabel>Zajemi samo trenutno pojavno okno</guilabel> pod "
"<guilabel>Možnosti</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Delay</guilabel> spin-box allows you to set the delay between "
"pressing the <guibutton>Take a New Screenshot</guibutton> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>) button and taking the "
"screenshot. This delay can be set in increments of 1 seconds using the "
"spinbox buttons or the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"V vrtilnem polju <guilabel>Zakasnitev</guilabel> lahko nastavite zamik med "
"pritiskom <guibutton>Naredi nov posnetek zaslona</guibutton> (<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap ></keycombo>) in naredite posnetek "
"zaslona. To zakasnitev lahko nastavite v korakih po 1 sekundo z uporabo "
"gumbov na zaslonu ali tipkovnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When taking a time-delayed screenshot, &spectacle; displays the remaining "
"time before the screenshot is taken in its window title, and makes it "
"visible in its Task Manager item. &spectacle;'s Task Manager button also "
"shows a progress bar, so you can keep track of when the snap will be taken."
msgstr ""
"Ko posnamete posnetek zaslona s časovnim zamikom, &spectacle; prikaže "
"preostali čas do posnetka zaslona v naslovu okna in ga naredi vidnega v "
"elementu upravitelja opravil. Gumb upravitelja opravil &spectacle; prikazuje "
"tudi vrstico napredka, tako da lahko spremljate, kdaj bo posnetek posnet."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While waiting for the delayed screenshot, you can un-minimize &spectacle; "
"and the <guibutton>Take a New Screenshot</guibutton> button will turn into a "
"<guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> button. The progress bar will also be shown "
"here, giving you the chance to stop the countdown."
msgstr ""
"Medtem ko čakate na zakasnjeni posnetek zaslona, lahko pomanjšate "
"&spectacle; in gumb <guibutton>Naredi nov posnetek zaslona</guibutton> se "
"spremeni v gumb <guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton>. Tukaj bo prikazana tudi "
"vrstica napredka, ki vam bo dala možnost, da ustavite odštevanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enabling the <guilabel>On Click</guilabel> checkbox overrides the delay. "
"When this checkbox is enabled, pressing the <guibutton>Take a New "
"Screenshot</guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo>) button hides the &spectacle; window and changes the mouse cursor "
"to a crosshair. The screenshot is captured when the mouse is left-clicked, "
"or aborted if any other mouse buttons are clicked. Note that you cannot "
"interact with the desktop using the mouse while the cursor is a crosshair, "
"but you can use the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Omogočanje potrditvenega polja <guilabel>Ob kliku</guilabel> preglasi "
"zakasnitev. Ko je to potrditveno polje omogočeno, s pritiskom gumba "
"<guibutton>Naredi nov posnetek zaslona</guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>) skrijete &spectacle; okno in "
"spremenite kazalec miške v križec. Posnetek zaslona se zajame, ko kliknete "
"levi gumb na miški, ali prekine, če kliknete kateri koli drug gumb miške. "
"Upoštevajte, da ne morete komunicirati z namizjem z miško, medtem ko je "
"kazalec križec, lahko pa uporabite tipkovnico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Možnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Options settings allow you to select whether the mouse cursor should be "
"included in the screenshots, and whether to capture window decorations along "
"with the image of a single application window. In <guilabel>Window Under "
"Cursor</guilabel> mode, it also allows you to select if &spectacle; shall "
"only capture the image of the current popup menu under the cursor, or also "
"include the parent window. Finally, <guilabel>Quit after Save or Copy</"
"guilabel> will quit &spectacle; after any save or copy operations."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve Možnosti vam omogočajo, da izberete, ali naj bo kazalec miške "
"vključen v posnetke zaslona in ali želite zajeti okraske oken skupaj s sliko "
"okna posamezne aplikacije. V načinu <guilabel>Okno pod kazalcem</guilabel> "
"omogoča tudi izbiro, če &spectacle; zajame samo sliko trenutnega pojavnega "
"menija pod kazalcem ali vključuje tudi nadrejeno okno. Končno, "
"<guilabel>Zapri po shranjevanju ali kopiranju</guilabel> zapre &spectacle; "
"po kakršnih koli operacijah shranjevanja ali kopiranja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enabling the <guilabel>Include mouse pointer</guilabel> checkbox includes an "
"image of the mouse pointer in the screenshot."
msgstr ""
"Omogočanje potrditvenega polja <guilabel>Vključi kazalec miške</guilabel> "
"vključuje sliko kazalca miške na posnetku zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Include window titlebar and borders</guilabel> option is only "
"enabled when either the <guilabel>Active Window</guilabel> mode or the "
"<guilabel>Window Under Cursor</guilabel> mode is selected in the "
"<guilabel>Area</guilabel> combo-box. Checking this option includes the "
"window borders and decoration in the screenshot, while unchecking it gives "
"an image of only the window contents."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Vključi naslovno vrstico in obrobe okna</guilabel> je "
"omogočena le, če je izbrana možnost <guilabel>Aktivno okno</guilabel> ali "
"način <guilabel>Okno pod kazalcem</guilabel> v kombiniranem polju "
"<guilabel>Območje</guilabel>. Če potrdite to možnost, vključite obrobe okna "
"in dekoracijo na posnetku zaslona, medtem ko jo izklopite, dobite sliko samo "
"vsebine okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Include window shadow</guilabel> option is only enabled when "
"either the <guilabel>Active Window</guilabel> mode or the <guilabel>Window "
"Under Cursor</guilabel> mode is selected in the <guilabel>Area</guilabel> "
"combo-box. Checking this option includes the window shadow in the "
"screenshot, while unchecking it gives an image of the window without the "
"shadow."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Vključi senco okna</guilabel> je omogočena le, ko je "
"izbran bodisi način <guilabel>Aktivno okno</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Okno pod "
"kazalcem</guilabel> v <guilabel>Območju</guilabel> kombiniranega polja. "
"Potrjena ta možnost vključuje senco okna v posnetek zaslona, nepotrjena pa "
"prikaže sliko okna brez sence."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Capture the current pop-up only</guilabel> option is only "
"enabled when the <guilabel>Window Under Cursor</guilabel> mode is selected "
"in the <guilabel>Area</guilabel> combo-box. Checking this option captures "
"only the popup menu under the cursor, without its parent window."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Zajemi samo trenutno pojavno okno</guilabel> je omogočena "
"le, če je v kombiniranem polju <guilabel>Območje</guilabel> izbran način "
"<guilabel>Okno pod kazalcem</guilabel>. Če izberete to možnost, zajamete "
"samo pojavni meni pod kazalcem, brez njegovega nadrejenega okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Quit after manual Save or Copy</guilabel> option will quit "
"&spectacle; after any saving or copying operations. Note that a copied "
"screenshot will only be retained if you are running a clipboard manager that "
"accepts images. KDE Klipper can be configured in this manner by right-"
"clicking on its icon, selecting <guilabel>Configure Clipboard...</guilabel>, "
"and unchecking <guilabel>Ignore images</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Zapri po ročnem shranjevanju ali kopiranju</guilabel> "
"zapre &spectacle; po kakršnem koli shranjevanju ali kopiranju. Upoštevajte, "
"da se bo kopiran posnetek zaslona ohranil le, če uporabljate upravitelja "
"odložišča, ki sprejema slike. KDE Klipper lahko konfigurirate na ta način "
"tako, da z desno miškino tipko kliknete njegovo ikono, izberete "
"<guilabel>Konfiguriraj odložišče...</guilabel> in počistite polje "
"<guilabel>Prezri slike</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Additional Functionality"
msgstr "Dodatna funkcionalnost"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Buttons"
msgstr "Gumbi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are some buttons located at the bottom of the &spectacle; window. "
"Their functions are described below:"
msgstr ""
"Na dnu okna &spectacle; je nekaj gumbov. Njihove funkcije so opisane spodaj:"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Gives you the common menu items described in the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; "
"Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Ponuja običajne elemente menija, opisane v <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html#menus-help\">meniju Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnovah."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure..."
msgstr "Konfiguriraj..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Gives you access to &spectacle;'s Configure window where you can change the "
"capture settings and default save location and filename."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vam dostop do okna za konfiguracijo &spectacle;, kjer lahko "
"spremenite nastavitve zajema ter privzeto mesto shranjevanja in ime datoteke."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Annotate"
msgstr "Opombe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens an annotation editor window that offers various annotating tools:"
msgstr "Odpre okno urejevalnika opomb, ki ponuja različna orodja za opombe:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Annotation editor"
msgstr "Urejevalnik opomb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Give a try to the annotating tools. You might find everything that is needed "
"to explain your screenshots there: arrows, pen, markers, text boxes, "
"numbers, even smileys. It is possible to change the tool parameters and add "
"effects (shadow, grayscale, and border)."
msgstr ""
"Preizkusite orodja za označevanje. Tam boste morda našli vse, kar "
"potrebujete za razlago vaših posnetkov zaslona: puščice, pero, oznake, "
"besedilna polja, številke, celo smeške. Možno je spreminjati parametre "
"orodja in dodajati učinke (senca, sivina in obroba)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you think that annotating is finished press the <guibutton>Annotation "
"Done</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ko menite, da je komentiranje končano, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Pripis "
"končan</guibutton>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tools"
msgstr "Orodja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a drop-down menu which offers various tools:"
msgstr "Odpre spustni meni, ki ponuja različna orodja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Open Default Screenshots Folder</guimenuitem> will highlight "
"the last saved screenshot in the default file manager"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Odpri privzeto mapo s posnetki zaslona</guimenuitem> bo označil "
"zadnji shranjen posnetek zaslona v privzetem upravitelju datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Access to the <guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem> dialog"
msgstr "Dostop do pogovornega okna <guimenuitem>Natisni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "A range of external programs for Screen Recording"
msgstr "Vrsta zunanjih programov za snemanje zaslona"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export"
msgstr "Izvozi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a drop-down menu that will allow you to directly open the screenshot "
"with all programs that are associated with the PNG (Portable Network "
"Graphics) &MIME; type. Depending on what programs are installed, you will be "
"able to open and edit the snapshot in your graphics applications or viewers."
msgstr ""
"Odpre spustni meni, ki vam omogoča, da neposredno odprete posnetek zaslona z "
"vsemi programi, ki so povezani s PNG (prenosna omrežna grafika) &MIME; "
"vrsto. Odvisno od nameščenih programov boste lahko odpirali in urejali "
"posnetek v svojih grafičnih aplikacijah ali pregledovalnikih."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy Image to Clipboard/Copy Location to Clipboard"
msgstr "Kopiraj sliko v odložišče/Kopiraj lokacijo v odložišče"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copies the current screenshot or its location to the clipboard. You can also "
"use the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> "
"keyboard shortcut for this."
msgstr ""
"Kopira trenutni posnetek zaslona ali njegovo lokacijo v odložišče. Za to "
"lahko uporabite tudi bližnjico na tipkovnici <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save As"
msgstr "Shrani kot"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saves the screenshot as a PNG image in your default Pictures folder and "
"immediately exits the application."
msgstr ""
"Shrani posnetek zaslona kot sliko PNG v privzeto mapo s slikami in takoj "
"zapre aplikacijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure"
msgstr "Konfiguriraj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>Configure...</guibutton> button to open the configuration "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <guibutton>Konfiguriraj...</guibutton>, da odprete "
"konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>General</title>"
msgstr "<title>Splošno</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>General</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Splošno</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "When launching Spectacle"
msgstr "Ob zagonu Spectacle"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows to <guilabel>Take full screen screenshot</guilabel>, use last-used "
"capture mode, or do not take a screenshot automatically. The last-used "
"capture mode is the one set in Capture Mode"
msgstr ""
"Omogoča <guilabel>posnetek celozaslonskega posnetka zaslona</guilabel>, "
"uporabo zadnjega uporabljenega načina zajema ali ne naredi samodejno "
"posnetka zaslona. Zadnji uporabljeni način zajemanja je tisti, ki je "
"nastavljen v načinu zajemanja"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "After taking a screenshot"
msgstr "Po posnetku zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows <guilabel>Save file to default folder</guilabel>, switching off any "
"clipboard actions, copying the image to clipboard, or copying screenshot "
"path to the clipboard. The default location can be configured using the "
"<link linkend=\"save-page\">Save</link> configuration page. It is possible "
"to <guilabel>Copy file location to clipboard</guilabel>. You can then paste "
"it anywhere that accepts text input. Note that you must be running a "
"clipboard manager in order to keep the path in the clipboard after "
"&spectacle; quits."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča <guilabel>Shraniti datoteko v privzeto mapo</guilabel>, izklop vseh "
"dejanj v odložišču, kopiranje slike v odložišče ali kopiranje poti posnetka "
"zaslona v odložišče. Privzeto lokacijo je mogoče konfigurirati s "
"konfiguracijsko stranjo <link linkend=\"save-page\">Shrani</link>. Možno je "
"<guilabel>Kopirati lokacijo datoteke v odložišče</guilabel>. Nato ga lahko "
"prilepite kamor koli, ki omogoča vnos besedila. Upoštevajte, da morate "
"zagnati upravitelja odložišča, da ohranite pot v odložišču ko &spectacle; "
"konča."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press screenshot key to"
msgstr "Pritisnite tipko za posnetek zaslona, da"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a shortcut to make screenshot is pressed and &spectacle; is already "
"running it is possible to configure the behavior of the screenshoting "
"system. You can choose between taking a new screenshot, opening of a new "
"&spectacle; window, and returning focus to the existing &spectacle; window."
msgstr ""
"Ko pritisnete bližnjico za izdelavo posnetka zaslona in &spectacle; že "
"deluje, je mogoče konfigurirati vedenje sistema za snemanje zaslona. "
"Izbirate lahko med ustvarjanjem novega posnetka zaslona, odpiranjem novega "
"&spectacle; okna in vrnitev fokusa na obstoječe &spectacle; okno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use light background"
msgstr "Uporabite svetlo ozadje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use a light background color to mask the cropped-out area in the rectangular "
"region selector. This may make dark cursors easier to see."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite svetlo barvo ozadja, da zakrijete izrezano območje v izbirniku "
"pravokotne regije. Tako boste lažje videli temne kazalce."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show magnifier"
msgstr "Prikaži lupo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a screenshot is saved, copy the location at which the file was saved to "
"the clipboard. You can then paste it anywhere that accepts text input. Note "
"that you must be running a clipboard manager in order to keep the path in "
"the clipboard after &spectacle; quits."
msgstr ""
"Ko je posnetek zaslona shranjen, kopirajte mesto, kjer je bila datoteka "
"shranjena, v odložišče. Nato ga lahko prilepite kamor koli, kjer je omogočen "
"vnos besedila. Upoštevajte, da morate zagnati upravitelja odložišča, da "
"ohranite pot v odložišču ko &spectacle; konča."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accept on click-and-release"
msgstr "Sprejmi, ko klikneš in spustiš"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, accept the selected region as soon as the mouse button is "
"released in the <guilabel>Rectangular Region</guilabel> mode."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, sprejme izbrano območje takoj, ko spustite miškino tipko v "
"načinu <guilabel>Pravokotna regija</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When selecting a new region, without a previously saved region available, "
"clicking, dragging, and releasing the mouse button should immediately "
"capture the selected region. When a previously saved region is shown, the "
"saved region can be manipulated further and saving this region requires "
"manual confirmation (&Enter; or double click with the &LMB;). Clicking and "
"dragging outside of the previously saved region captures the newly selected "
"region immediately."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete novo regijo, brez predhodno shranjene regije, morate s klikom, "
"vlečenjem in sprostitvijo gumba miške takoj zajeti izbrano regijo. Ko je "
"prikazano predhodno shranjeno območje, je s shranjenim območjem mogoče "
"nadalje manipulirati, shranjevanje tega območja pa zahteva ročno potrditev "
"(&Enter; ali dvojni klik z levim klikom miške). Če kliknete in povlečete "
"izven predhodno shranjene regije, takoj zajamete novo izbrano regijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remember selected area"
msgstr "Zapomni si izbrano območje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, &spectacle; remembers an initial selection when you take a "
"screenshot of a rectangular region until you close the &spectacle; window. "
"You can also choose to make &spectacle; never remember selected area or "
"remember it between the screenshoting sessions."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto si &spectacle; zapomni začetni izbor, ko posnamete posnetek zaslona "
"pravokotnega območja, dokler ne zaprete okna &spectacle;. Izberete lahko "
"tudi da si &spectacle; nikoli ne zapomni izbranega območja ali pa si ga "
"zapomni med sejami snemanja zaslona."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Save</title>"
msgstr "<title>Shrani</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you use the <guilabel>Save</guilabel> function, &spectacle; saves the "
"image with a default filename, in your Pictures folder (which is inside your "
"home folder). The default filename includes the date and time when the image "
"was taken."
msgstr ""
"Ko uporabite funkcijo <guilabel>Shrani</guilabel>, &spectacle; shrani sliko "
"s privzetim imenom datoteke v mapo Slike (ki je v domači mapi). Privzeto ime "
"datoteke vključuje datum in čas, ko je bila slika posneta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Save</guilabel> page allows you to set the default save "
"location and filename. Clicking this option brings up a dialog box like the "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"Stran <guilabel>Shrani</guilabel> vam omogoča, da nastavite privzeto mesto "
"shranjevanja in ime datoteke. Če kliknete to možnost, se odpre tako "
"pogovorno okno:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Save</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Shrani</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Location"
msgstr "Shrani lokacijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the location text box set the folder where you'd like to save your "
"screenshots when you press <guibutton>Save</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"V besedilnem polju lokacije nastavite mapo, kamor želite shraniti posnetke "
"zaslona, ko pritisnete <guibutton>Shrani</guibutton>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compression Quality"
msgstr "Kakovost stiskanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the image quality when saving with lossy image formats like JPEG. The "
"higher values give better quality but increase the file size. See <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Image_file_formats\">Wikipedia page</ulink> "
"for the details on the image formats that are used in &spectacle;."
msgstr ""
"Izberite kakovost slike pri shranjevanju s formati slik z izgubo, kot je "
"JPEG. Višje vrednosti dajejo boljšo kakovost, vendar povečajo velikost "
"datoteke. Oglejte si <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Image_file_formats\">stran Wikipedije</ulink> za podrobnosti o formatih "
"slik, ki se uporabljajo v &spectacle;-u."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filename"
msgstr "Ime datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set a default filename for saved screenshots."
msgstr "Nastavite privzeto ime datoteke za shranjene posnetke zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the following placeholders in the filename, which will be "
"replaced with actual text when the file is saved:"
msgstr ""
"V imenu datoteke lahko uporabite naslednje ogradne oznake, ki bodo zamenjane "
"z dejanskim besedilom, ko bo datoteka shranjena:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;dd&gt;</userinput>: Day"
msgstr "<userinput>&lt;dd&gt;</userinput>: Dan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;hh&gt;</userinput>: Hour"
msgstr "<userinput>&lt;hh&gt;</userinput>: Ura"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;MM&gt;</userinput>: Month"
msgstr "<userinput>&lt;MM&gt;</userinput>: Mesec"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;ss&gt;</userinput>: Second"
msgstr "<userinput>&lt;ss&gt;</userinput>: Sekunda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;title&gt;</userinput>: Window title"
msgstr "<userinput>&lt;title&gt;</userinput>: Naslov okna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;yyyy&gt;</userinput>: Year (4 digit)"
msgstr "<userinput>&lt;yyyy&gt;</userinput>: Leto (4-mestno)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;#&gt;</userinput>: Sequential number"
msgstr "<userinput>&lt;#&gt;</userinput>: Zaporedna številka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;mm&gt;</userinput>: Minute"
msgstr "<userinput>&lt;mm&gt;</userinput>: Minuta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>&lt;yy&gt;</userinput>: Year (2 digit)"
msgstr "<userinput>&lt;yy&gt;</userinput>: Leto (2 števki)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can click on placeholders in the reference list below to insert them "
"into the <guilabel>Filename</guilabel> line."
msgstr ""
"Lahko kliknete ogradne oznake na spodnjem seznamu referenc, da jih vstavite "
"v vrstico <guilabel>Ime datoteke</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a file with this name already exists, a serial number will be appended to "
"the filename. For example, if the filename is <filename>Screenshot</"
"filename>, and <filename>Screenshot.png</filename> already exists, the image "
"will be saved as <filename>Screenshot-1.png</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Če datoteka s tem imenom že obstaja, bo imenu datoteke dodana serijska "
"številka. Če je na primer ime datoteke <filename>Screenshot.png</filename> "
"in <filename>Screenshot.png</filename> že obstaja, bo slika shranjena kot "
"<filename>Screenshot-1.png</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the drop-down box next to the text field to select the default image "
"format for screenshots. See <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Image_file_formats\">Wikipedia page</ulink> for the details on the image "
"formats that are used in &spectacle;."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite spustno polje poleg besedilnega polja, da izberete privzeti format "
"slike za posnetke zaslona. Oglejte si <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Image_file_formats\">stran Wikipedije</ulink> za podrobnosti o formatih "
"slik, ki se uporabljajo v &spectacle;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "Bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This configuration page can be used to change the default shortcuts of "
"&spectacle;. It is possible to configure shortcuts for starting &spectacle; "
"and capturing different parts of your desktop."
msgstr ""
"To konfiguracijsko stran lahko uporabite za spreminjanje privzetih bližnjic "
"&spectacle;. Možno je konfigurirati bližnjice za zagon &spectacle; in zajem "
"različnih delov namizja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag and Drop"
msgstr "Povleci in spusti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A captured image can be dragged to another application or document. If the "
"application is able to handle images, a copy of the full image is inserted "
"there."
msgstr ""
"Zajeto sliko lahko povlečete v drugo aplikacijo ali dokument. Če aplikacija "
"lahko obdeluje slike, se tja vstavi kopija celotne slike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you drag a screenshot into a file manager window, a dialog pops up where "
"you can edit the filename and select the image format and the file will be "
"inserted into the actual folder."
msgstr ""
"Če povlečete posnetek zaslona v okno upravitelja datotek, se prikaže "
"pogovorno okno, kjer lahko uredite ime datoteke in izberete obliko slike, "
"datoteka pa bo vstavljena v dejansko mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you drag the screenshot to a text box, the path to the temporary saved "
"file is inserted. This is useful for example to upload a screenshot through "
"web forms or to attach screenshots into bug reports on the <ulink url="
"\"https://bugs.kde.org/\">&kde; bugtracker</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če povlečete posnetek zaslona v besedilno polje, se vstavi pot do začasno "
"shranjene datoteke. To je uporabno na primer za nalaganje posnetka zaslona "
"prek spletnih obrazcev ali pripenjanje posnetkov zaslona v poročila o "
"napakah na <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/\">&kde;-jevem sledilniku "
"hroščev</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This works with all clients that do not pick up the image data, but only "
"look for a &URL; in the dragged mimedata."
msgstr ""
"To deluje z vsemi odjemalci, ki ne poberejo slikovnih podatkov, ampak samo "
"iščejo &URL; v vlečenih mime-podatkih."

